            </p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="content-2">
        <div class="highlight-section">
            <div class="highlight-title">
                <span>HIGHLIGHT</span> <br>
                <h2 class="featured-products">FEATURED PRODUCTS</h2>
            </div>
            <button class="see-all">See all</button>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <button class="product">
                <img src="~/images/pr4.png" alt="Chanel Coco Mademoiselle">
                <div class="product-title">Nước hoa Chanel Coco Mademoiselle EDP Intense</div>
                <div class="price">1000$ US</div>
            </button>
            <button class="product">
